a:5:{s:5:"title";s:50:"Salesmate adds more informative SMS failure errors";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:371:"<p>When SMS sending fails from the provider side, Salesmate now shows clearer failure reasons with context to speed up troubleshooting.</p>
<p>Where to find it: Text Messaging → Delivery/Failure status view.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/">https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/</a></p>
